steps.html_instructions: Head east on E San Francisco St toward Cathedral Pl
Take the 1st left onto Old Santa Fe Trail
Take the Interstate 25 N ramp to Las Vegas/US 285 S/Clines Corners

Merge onto I-25 N/US-285 S
Continue to follow I-25 N
Entering Colorado
Take exit Exit 15 toward US-160 E/Kit Carson Trail

Turn right onto 160 Hwy Bypass/E Goddard Ave (signs for Kit Carson Tr)
Continue to follow 160 Hwy Bypass

Turn left onto US-350 E/E Main St
Continue to follow US-350 E
Turn right onto CO-71 N/I-70BUS E/US-24 E/U.S. 287 S/US-40 E/Main St (signs for Colorado 71 N)

Turn left onto CO-71 N/1st Ave
Continue to follow CO-71 N

Slight right to merge onto I-76 E
Entering Nebraska

Take exit 177 to merge onto US-83 N/S Dewey St toward N Platte
Continue to follow US-83 N

Turn left onto US-83 N/W 4th St
Continue to follow US-83 N
Entering South Dakota

Turn left onto US-18 W/US-83 N/2nd St
Continue to follow US-18 W/US-83 N
Turn right to merge onto I-90 E/US-83 N

Turn left onto SD-53 N/US-83 N
Continue to follow US-83 N
S Pierre St turns right and becomes E Pleasant Dr

Turn left onto S Euclid Ave
Destination will be on the left
